bhakti_rasamrta_sindhu.translation:
However, the combination of two unfriendly rasas will not produce distaste under the following conditions:

where one of the two conflicting rasas is negated by a statement;

where two conflicting rasas are present through remembrance;

where two rasas are compared;

where a friendly or neutral rasa intervenes between two conflicting rasas;

where the viṣayas or āśrayas of two conflicting rasas (one of which is a secondary rasa) are different.
